I'll take my Death, I think you are hand&s;omer&mdash;and within a
Year or two as young.&mdash;If you cou'd but &s;tay for me, I &s;hou'd
overtake you&mdash;But that cannot be&mdash;Well, that Thought
makes me melan$holy&mdash;Now I'll be &s;ad.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mrs. Mar.</SPEAKER>
<P>Your merry Note may be chang'd &s;ooner than you
think.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Milla.</SPEAKER>
<P>D'ye &s;ay &s;o? Then I'm re&s;olv'd I'll have a Song to keep
