</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Pet.</SPEAKER>
<P>Ay in the main&mdash;But when I have a Humour to con|tradict.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Wit.</SPEAKER>
<P>Ay, when he has a Humour to contradict, then I contra|dict
