<PB N="35" REF="42">
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Wit.</SPEAKER>
<P>That I confe&s;s I wonder at too.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Milla.</SPEAKER>
<P>Ah! to marry an Ignorant! that can hardly Read or
