</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady.</SPEAKER>
<P>O dear Friend, I am &s;o a&s;ham'd that you &s;hould meet with
&s;uch Returns;&mdash;You ought to ask Pardon on your Knees,
ungrateful Creature; &s;he de&s;erves more from you, than all your
