<HI>Cow-Itch.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady.</SPEAKER>
<P>O, 'tis very hard!</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mrs. Mar.</SPEAKER>
<P>And then to have my Young Revellers of the
