<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lady.</SPEAKER>
<P>Wor&s;e and wor&s;e.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Mrs. Mar.</SPEAKER>
<P>Nay this is nothing; if it would end here 'twere
